'''阿奇霉素'''（Azithromycin, {{IPAc-en|ə|ˌ|z|ɪ|θ|r|oʊ|ˈ|m|aɪ|s|ɨ|n}} <ref name=":0">[http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/azithromycin Entry "azithromycin" in Merriam-Webster Online Dictionary] {{Wayback|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/azithromycin |date=20190713084702 }}.</ref>）是一种屬於[[大环内酯|大环内酯]]的[[抗生素|抗生素]]，於1980年被發現，1981年推出。又翻译作'''阿红霉素'''、'''阿齐红霉素'''。阿奇黴素是一種用以治療許多[[细菌|细菌]]感染的[[抗细菌药|抗细菌药]]<ref name=":0" />，包含[[中耳炎|中耳炎]]、[[链球菌性咽炎|链球菌性咽炎]]、[[肺炎|肺炎]]、[[旅行者腹瀉|旅行者腹瀉]]以及其他病症如[[腸胃炎|腸胃炎]]，也可治療許多[[性傳染病|性傳染病]]，包含[[衣原體門|衣原體]]感染疾病和[[淋病|淋病]]，另外也可用以治療[[疟疾|疟疾]]。阿奇黴素的投藥方式有口服或[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]，一天僅限用一劑。<ref name=":0" />

常見的副作用包含[[恶心|恶心]]、[[呕吐|呕吐]]、[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]及食慾不振，也可能引發過敏反應或一種腹瀉疾病--[[偽膜性結腸炎|偽膜性結腸炎]]， 目前未能斷言對[[母乳餵養|母乳餵養]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.drugs.com/breastfeeding/azithromycin.html|title=Azithromycin use while Breastfeeding|accessdate=4 September 2015|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905170054/http://www.drugs.com/breastfeeding/azithromycin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 患者是否有不良影響，但目前看來傾向於無虞<ref name=":1" />；對懷孕患者則未發現不良影響<ref name=":0" />。阿奇黴素是Azalide藥物，屬於一種[[大環內酯|大環內酯]]的抗細菌藥，藉由降低蛋白質生成以抑制細菌增殖。<ref name=":0" />

1980年阿奇黴素問世<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/801405589|last=1935-|first=Greenwood, David,|date=2008-01-01|publisher=Oxford University Press|chapter=Antimicrobial drugs : chronicle of a twentieth century medical triumph|oclc=801405589|title=|access-date=2016-12-16|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713084707/https://www.worldcat.org/title/antimicrobial-drugs-chronicle-of-a-twentieth-century-medical-triumph/oclc/801405589|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，並在[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]登錄有案<ref>{{Cite web|url="WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|title=WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|accessdate=22 April 2014|author=|date=October 2013|publisher=World Health Organization}}</ref>，作為[[通用名药物|通用名药物]]的價格也十分親民<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/922644939|date=2014-01-01|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|chapter=Tarascon pocket pharmacopoeia 2015 deluxe lab coat edition.|oclc=922644939|title=|access-date=2016-12-16|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713084658/https://www.worldcat.org/title/tarascon-pocket-pharmacopoeia-2015-deluxe-lab-coat-edition/oclc/922644939|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，一劑批發價約在0.18-2.98美元左右<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=AZI500T&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=500%20mg&desc=Azithromycin&pack=new&frm=TAB-CAP&rte=PO&class_code2=06%2E2%2E2%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2806%2E2%2E2%2E%29Other%20antibacterials%3Cbr%3E|title=Azithromycin|accessdate=4 September 2015|author=|date=|publisher=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|archive-date=2020-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324120319/https://shortener.secureserver.net/error_404|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；在美國，截止2018年的每疗程花费约为4美元。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://data.medicaid.gov/Drug-Pricing-and-Payment/NADAC-as-of-2018-05-23/5kr5-j2di|title=National Average Drug Acquisition Cost (NADAC) Retrieved 24 May 2018.|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=Centers for Medicare 